# Feedback & Corrections

This file is a living document. It grows over time as the human corrects the AI during development sessions.

## How This Works

When the human says any of the following (or similar):
- "Remember this for next time"
- "Don't do that again"
- "Always do it this way"
- "I prefer X over Y"
- "That was wrong because..."
- "From now on..."

**The AI must**:
1. Acknowledge the correction.
2. Append a new entry to the "Learned Corrections" section below, with the date and a concise rule.
3. Follow the correction in all future work.

When starting any new task, scan the entries below first.

